name: TAGGED  YOU'RE  IT  KINDNESS  CARDS
description:
TAGGED  YOU'RE IT KINDNESS CARDS -5 PACK

* * HOW TO USE * *
1. Do a KIND ACT for someone.
2. Give them a TYI KINDNESS CARD, and encourage them to pass on a KIND ACT to someone else.
3. Share your story on our TAGGED YOU'RE IT Facebook page http://www.facebook.com/tagged.youreit.3  to help inspire others.
4.  Be the POSITIVE CHANGE, one KIND ACT at a time.

name: TAGGED YOU'RE IT GLOBAL KINDNESS TO WILDLIFE AND NATURE TAG TEAM MBER NECKLACE
description:
You've Been TAGGED.  Now YOU'RE IT !  Wear this cool TAGGED YOU'RE IT necklace to show your support, and help spread and promote GLOBAL KINDNESS TO WILDLIFE AND NATURE everywhere.  Necklace displays our signature TAGGED YOU'RE IT GLOBAL KINDNESS TO WILDLIFE AND NATURE logo on front.  TAG TEAM MEMBER identification on back.  Comes on adjustable length cord, made from soda pop bottles.  Buy Two.  Keep one for yourself.  And pass the second on to the recipient of your Kind Deed.

"Come TAG in the FUN.  Help Spread the Spirit of KINDNESS to Everyone.  Do a KIND DEED for someone in NEED.  Pass this TYI necklace on to keep the Circle of Kindness going.  Share your experience on our TYI Facebook page http://www.facebook.com/taggedyoureit.3   And you will Help Inspire Global Kindness and the outpouring of Love, Friendship and Unity throughout the world.
